的感情很好，以往每逢農曆新年，買年花、擺攢盒（全盒）及團年飯等大小應節事宜，均由母親一手包辦、安排妥當，全家一起過年。他坦言母親離世令家人心情大受影響，今年因新年「撞白事」令全家無意慶祝，「冷冷清清咁」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：家屬質疑瑪嘉烈醫院違急救協議 延救病母終不治捱不過年關<br />\n<br />\n記者：何家朗"},{"pid":"6d22f1e27ed34f0979ec958d9d297897d37596cf","tid":1013116,"uid":28628,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"真係好撚on9 <br />\n人地醫生都講明無irreversible change <br />\n遲早走<br />\n拔喉無呼吸可以唔救<br />\n之後有呼吸就要救<br />\n但只限去到初7 <br />\n乜撚野logic 嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔好撚講 <br />\n初135可以救<br />\n初246唔比救<br />\n玩具咩<br />\n<br />\n有無尊重過病人<br />\n有無尊重過生命<br />\n完全物化緊條人命"},{"pid":"2c9f083370d75e9ac5d0524081b536539f027b86","tid":1013116,"uid":142532,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/f1/Moknowisdom.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20071014044424\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff1%2FMoknowisdom.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20071014044424&h=803e3b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/38/Mok1comicsgif1.gif/revision/latest?cb=20070729135825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F38%2FMok1comicsgif1.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070729135825&h=e8abfa7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"766e015ba406798acaa35bbc310e5684bcf1092d","tid":1013116,"uid":100766,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:21:24.000Z","msg":"好多人都過唔到年架啦<br />\n臨近年尾，下面要交數架<br />\n今年輪到佢咪帶佢走囉...."},{"pid":"e2beb9daceb9cfcf659da86e1cbca676a267be4d","tid":1013116,"uid":32407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"79fad3df4c9aae0e20f1bae28dc2ecb75392b9fd","tid":1013116,"uid":2772,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"過到年關又點<br />\n有獎?"},"citedBy":0,"